{"tid":490683,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人C Drive長期無容量","createTime":"2017-12-06T00:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T05:05:11.000Z","uid":43718,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae34d581315b65745444fef0746aa6353210f93","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:02:38.000Z","msg":"明明已經無咩野裝係C Drive<br />\n但成日無啦啦都會無位<br />\n而家長期得6, 7GB <br />\n有時長機會多D 有時會少D<br />\n有無人知可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0083de1f694d1577129f169f1fac9008c77eb5","tid":490683,"uid":52727,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:04:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.azofreeware.com/2007/08/treesize-free-21082.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.azofreeware.com%2F2007%2F08%2Ftreesize-free-21082.html%3Fm%3D1&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7747e2fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.azofreeware.com/2007/08/treesize-free-21082.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n用佢睇下咩野佔咗咁多位"},{"pid":"93eb5c9ce5ca7da1fdaa8b74b5ed753f320dc61b","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f39217dd6917b904eec5043720772e1d84bef90","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3004fac86adce21a8d7b079012fe6e426d0e380a","tid":490683,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:52:27.000Z","msg":"我記得高登流傳過一個delete 垃圾file嘅script, 你可以搵搵"},{"pid":"4625d66b965cd465efcbae5276d2b68ba0d9a5e2","tid":490683,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得高登流傳過一個delete 垃圾file嘅script, 你可以搵搵</blockquote><br />\n你指佢？<br />\n<br />\n@echo off<br />\necho 正在清除系統垃圾檔案中，請稍候......<br />\necho Angus福利社 <a href=\"http://wuangus.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwuangus.cc&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6f20dc30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wuangus.cc</a><br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.tmp<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*._mp<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.log<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.gid<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.chk<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.old<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\recycled\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%\\*.bak<br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%\\prefetch\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%\\cookies\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%\\recent\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temporary Internet Files\\*.*&quot;<br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temp\\*.*&quot;<br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%\\recent\\*.*&quot;<br />\nDEL /S /F /Q &quot;%systemroot%\\Temp\\*.*&quot;<br />\nDEL /S /F /Q &quot;%AllUsersProfile%\\「開始」功能表\\程式集\\Windows Messenger.lnk&quot;<br />\nRD /S /Q %windir%\\temp &amp; md %windir%\\temp<br />\nRD /S /Q &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temp&quot;<br />\nMD &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temp&quot;<br />\nRD /S /Q &quot;%systemdrive%\\Program Files\\Temp&quot;<br />\nMD &quot;%systemdrive%\\Program Files\\Temp&quot;<br />\nRD /S /Q &quot;%systemdrive%\\d&quot;<br />\nnet user aspnet /delete<br />\ncleanmgr /sagerun:99<br />\necho 清除系統垃圾檔案完成！<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔覺係垃圾太多 加上bat有風險<br />\n如：del /f /q %userprofile%\\*.*"},{"pid":"5846d385302d07eed8de94e6bf001d24416b09c9","tid":490683,"uid":887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:13:15.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你iTunes backup放左係c drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424fa34155574e0ff5f65b011d3534b471b1d208","tid":490683,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"冇c drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de86cbb0f6be2d2883c939f23513d94814e275dc","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係你iTunes backup放左係c drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔係<br />\n因為我無backup過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624743d5f14fcc09c19476fc8d0ee7caea7febdc","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ae4a5086851bd0cfed4dae1adb190560a2e34b","tid":490683,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"容量係用唔用都有咁多<br />\n你講既係空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d92b9c0c27fff4cb1f3b24892deabd9fd5a46bd","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>容量係用唔用都有咁多<br />\n你講既係空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c09fcd4b0adb62facd20d2b399b9a7eb22af2f9","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af6678acad10964b6a43087284ee3b619881f8f","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37010b66b1046a1d5956438a25365506cad6ec61","tid":490683,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"用 linux"},{"pid":"99c812911880a4c8740976e545f6ae05822faa9f","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T21:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用 linux</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4847fe5bb830544271aef0afe7f1d067622ae792","tid":490683,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T22:27:43.000Z","msg":"用CCleaner清位，之前都係咁，清完就多幾十gb"},{"pid":"752757e857b19036e03dd4dcb19d459398cf9caf","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T22:28:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用CCleaner清位，之前都係咁，清完就多幾十gb</blockquote><br />\n有用<br />\n都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ce0caf95037d64452cac8c320df6c6acf89248","tid":490683,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T22:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324a08ba862695f406b689cd3dab7fe8bb87db89","tid":490683,"uid":155558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"首先你本身C drive有幾大？ SSD？（SSD通常細）<br />\n另外再睇睇個paging file settings。  係咪放喺C，有幾大？<br />\n如果本身C drive 係細就set細啲，或改去其他drive。<br />\n再喺Cmd prompt打下dir 睇埋sub folder。<br />\n搵吓咩file size 係大，或不尋常多。<br />\n如果係近期先變少，sort埋file date，<br />\n睇睇邊啲軟件folder 近期generate 咁多可疑file。<br />\n仲有一招搵個掃毒軟件掃描吓有無中毒。"},{"pid":"2813d3906cb0797d305f01a65341818e8201d456","tid":490683,"uid":81703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"關咗個糸統還原"},{"pid":"2e8f159d9ba1b2545875fdb6e11892ca23353e59","tid":490683,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"係咪用win7<br />\n之前上網睇你RAM幾大佢就佢用番幾大既位做Buffer<br />\n你google下可以熄左佢"},{"pid":"ef66ed47d510e6c997880af528a46a7bc92dc002","tid":490683,"uid":67640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"如果係ios 其他佔左80g, 但我冇down好多野。咁點check?"},{"pid":"6bc26976ccde6c779f9fa9349c2b2335eff59613","tid":490683,"uid":33357,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我記得高登流傳過一個delete 垃圾file嘅script, 你可以搵搵</blockquote><br />\n你指佢？<br />\n<br />\n@echo off<br />\necho 正在清除系統垃圾檔案中，請稍候......<br />\necho Angus福利社 <a href=\"http://wuangus.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwuangus.cc&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6f20dc30\" target=\"_blank\">http://wuangus.cc</a><br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.tmp<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*._mp<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.log<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.gid<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.chk<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\*.old<br />\ndel /f /s /q %systemdrive%\\recycled\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%\\*.bak<br />\ndel /f /s /q %windir%\\prefetch\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%\\cookies\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /q %userprofile%\\recent\\*.*<br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temporary Internet Files\\*.*&quot;<br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temp\\*.*&quot;<br />\ndel /f /s /q &quot;%userprofile%\\recent\\*.*&quot;<br />\nDEL /S /F /Q &quot;%systemroot%\\Temp\\*.*&quot;<br />\nDEL /S /F /Q &quot;%AllUsersProfile%\\「開始」功能表\\程式集\\Windows Messenger.lnk&quot;<br />\nRD /S /Q %windir%\\temp &amp; md %windir%\\temp<br />\nRD /S /Q &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temp&quot;<br />\nMD &quot;%userprofile%\\Local Settings\\Temp&quot;<br />\nRD /S /Q &quot;%systemdrive%\\Program Files\\Temp&quot;<br />\nMD &quot;%systemdrive%\\Program Files\\Temp&quot;<br />\nRD /S /Q &quot;%systemdrive%\\d&quot;<br />\nnet user aspnet /delete<br />\ncleanmgr /sagerun:99<br />\necho 清除系統垃圾檔案完成！<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔覺係垃圾太多 加上bat有風險<br />\n如：del /f /q %userprofile%\\*.*</blockquote><br />\n有隻超級加強版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f3a9ab7cb6c7161053f6446464753101af14b4","tid":490683,"uid":68141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"今朝清完 2GB上返7GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}